ps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady-gaga-joker@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady-gaga-joker@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady-gaga-joker@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady-gaga-joker@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/joker-folie-a-deux">《小丑：双人舞》中饰演哈莉·奎恩的造型</a>受到了查尔斯·曼森的追随者的启发——请参阅下面导演托德·菲利普斯的评价。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="314" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/joker-review-a-melancholic-psychodrama-punctuated-by-splashes-of-shocking-violence-2543865#"><b>《小丑》评论：一部忧郁的心理剧，中间夹杂着令人震惊的暴力事件</b></a></li></ul><p>菲利普斯在接受<a href="https://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/lady-gaga-joker-folie-a-deux-unlike-anything-exclusive/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《帝国》杂志</em></a>采访时谈到了 Gaga 对这个角色的看法。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/margot-robbie">玛格特·罗比</a>此前曾在 2016 年的<em>《自杀小队》</em> 、她自己的衍生剧<em>《猛禽小队》</em>和 2021 年重启的<em>《自杀小队》</em>中扮演过这个角色。</p><p> Gaga 版本的哈莉·奎因将是一个截然不同的角色。菲利普斯说：“虽然人们会觉得她有些熟悉，但这确实是 Gaga 自己的诠释，也是斯科特（西尔弗，合著者）和我的诠释。” </p><figure id="attachment_3772890" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3772890" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3772890" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady_gaga_harley.jpg" alt="Lady Gaga 饰演 哈莉·奎茵" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady_gaga_harley.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady_gaga_harley-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady_gaga_harley-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady_gaga_harley-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady_gaga_harley-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady_gaga_harley-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3772890" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年 3 月 25 日，Lady Gaga 在《Joker: Folie a Deux》片场。（摄影：MEGA/GC Images）</figcaption></figure><p>他接着解释道：“她成为了[查尔斯]曼森让女孩们崇拜他的方式。有时这些[被监禁的杀人犯]会受到人们的尊敬。电影中关于哈雷的一些东西取自漫画书，但我们将其按照我们想要的方式塑造。”</p><p>在与<em>Empire的</em>聊天中，Gaga还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/lady-gaga-explains-how-she-had-to-change-her-singing-voice-for-joker-folie-a-deux-3778246">解释了她如何改变自己的歌声来扮演这个角色</a>。 “人们通过我的艺名 Lady Gaga 认识我，对吗？那是我作为表演者，但这不是这部电影的内容；这就是我的表演。我正在扮演一个角色，”她说。</p><p> “所以我在唱歌的方式上做了很多努力，让我的演唱方式来自于李，而不是来自于我作为一个表演者。” </p><figure id="attachment_3615824" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3615824" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3615824" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Joker-trailer-Folie-a-Deux.jpg" alt="双人舞曲" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Joker-trailer-Folie-a-Deux.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Joker-trailer-Folie-a-Deux-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Joker-trailer-Folie-a-Deux-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Joker-trailer-Folie-a-Deux-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Joker-trailer-Folie-a-Deux-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Joker-trailer-Folie-a-Deux-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3615824" class="wp-caption-text">杰昆·菲尼克斯 (Joaquin Phoenix) 和 Lady Gaga 在《小丑：双人舞曲》(Joker: Folie à Deux) 中亮相 图片来源：华纳兄弟/新闻稿</figcaption></figure><p><em>《小丑：双人舞》</em>讲述华金·菲尼克斯饰演的亚瑟·弗莱克/小丑在阿卡姆州立医院被监禁期间与音乐治疗师会面的故事。两人坠入爱河，弗莱克获释后，两人开始了一场注定的浪漫灾难。</p><p>本月早些时候，《Folie à Deux》的选角总监弗朗辛·麦斯勒 (Francine Maisler) 表示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/lady-gaga-will-blow-your-mind-in-joker-folie-a-deux-says-casting-director-3772881">Gaga 饰演的哈雷将“让你大吃一惊”</a> ，并补充说，她“真的很惊讶”这位歌手在电影拍摄期间能够与菲尼克斯保持同步。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/lady-gagas-harley-quinn-in-joker-folie-a-deux-is-inspired-by-charles-mansons-followers-3778665">《Joker: Folie à Deux》中 Lady Gaga 饰演的 Harley Quinn 的灵感源自 Charles Manson 的追随者，</a>最早出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Ravyn Lenae 邀请 Childish Gambino 创作新单曲《One Wish》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/ravyn-lenae-enlists-childish-gambino-for-new-single-one-wish-3778661?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=ravyn-lenae-enlists-childish-甘比诺新单一愿望Surej SinghMon, 29 Jul 2024 04:17:02 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3778661 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ravyn-lenae-childish-gambino@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Ravyn Lenae 和 Childish Gambino 的合成图像" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ravyn-lenae-childish-gambino@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ravyn-lenae-childish-gambino@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ravyn-lenae-childish-gambino@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ravyn-lenae-childish-gambino@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ravyn-lenae-childish-gambino@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ravyn-lenae-childish-gambino@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>本月早些时候，唐纳德·格洛弗 (Donald Glover) 以“Childish Gambino”的身份发行了他的最后一张专辑。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ravyn-lenae-enlists-childish-gambino-for-new-single-one-wish-3778661">Ravyn Lenae 邀请 Childish Gambino 创作新单曲《One Wish》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ravyn-lenae-childish-gambino@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Ravyn Lenae 和 Childish Gambino 的合成图像" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ravyn-lenae-childish-gambino@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ravyn-lenae-childish-gambino@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ravyn-lenae-childish-gambino@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ravyn-lenae-childish-gambino@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ravyn-lenae-childish-gambino@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ravyn-lenae-childish-gambino@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Ravyn Lenae 分享了一首新单曲“One Wish”，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/childish-gambino">Childish Gambino</a>合作 - 请听下面的内容。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/childish-gambino-bando-stone-and-the-new-world-review-a-bittersweet-send-off-to-a-musical-innovator-3776877">幼稚的甘比诺——《坂东石与新世界》评论：对音乐创新者苦乐参半的送别</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首单曲于周五（7 月 26 日）发行，一周前，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/donald-glover">唐纳德·格洛弗</a>（Donald Glover，又名“幼稚甘比诺”）以该绰号发行了他的最后一张专辑。 《One Wish》将成为芝加哥歌手兼作曲家 Lenae 即将推出的第二张专辑《Bird&#39;s Eye》的一部分。</p><p> 《Bird&#39;s Eye》将于 8 月 9 日通过大西洋唱片公司发行，现已<a href="https://ravynlenae.lnk.to/BirdsEye" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在数字平台上接受预订和预保存</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Ravyn Lenae - 一个愿望壮举。幼稚的甘比诺（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4oNYTgzNEPQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《One Wish》是继 Ty Dolla $ign 合作的《Love Is Blind》、《Love Me Not》和《Dream Girl》之后，《Bird&#39;s Eye》推出的第四首单曲。</p><p> 《One Wish》发行后，格洛弗在社交媒体上分享说，他与莱娜录制了另一首歌曲，希望有一天能发行。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我喜欢和<a href="https://twitter.com/ravynlenae?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@ravynlenae</a>一起工作</p><p>她的和声选择是顶级的。</p><p>我们还有另一首歌，希望有一天我能推出。</p><p> - 唐纳德 (@donaldglover) <a href="https://twitter.com/donaldglover/status/1816623127516057845?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 7 月 25 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>此前，格洛弗还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-childish-gambinos-unsettling-music-video-for-lithonia-3777026">发布了令人不安的“Lithonia”音乐录影带</a>。 《Lithonia》是格洛弗最后一张专辑中的第一首单曲，其昵称是“Bando Stone and The New World”。这张专辑于本月早些时候发行，同时也是一部同名新电影的官方原声带。唐纳德·格洛弗最近<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V44EenldJQs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">透露了这部电影的预告片</a>，尽管该电影尚未确定上映日期。</p><p> Kyann-Syan Williams 在<em>NME</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/childish-gambino-bando-stone-and-the-new-world-review-a-bittersweet-send-off-to-a-musical-innovator-3776877">四星评论</a>中写道：“Glover 创造了一张与他其他作品一样超凡脱俗的唱片。然而，“班多·斯通（Bando Stone）和新世界”（Bando Stone and the New World）略微跌跌撞撞 - 与他以前的作品相比，它的声音品种令人兴奋，它缺乏明显的凝聚力或主题感 - 使其与幼稚的甘比诺传说中的传奇告别。” </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-childish-gambinos-unsettling-music-video-for-lithonia-3777026"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>在专辑发行之前，格洛弗（Glover） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/donald-glover-explains-why-hes-retiring-the-childish-gambino-moniker-3775910">解释了为什么他要退休幼稚的甘比诺（Chalking Gambino）</a> ，将其归结为描绘说唱歌手不再“实现”，并想在父亲和父亲和父亲去世后将更多的时间用于他的个人生活和其他途径他的孩子的出生。</p></div></div><p> Ravyn Lenae邮<a href="https://www.nme.com">报</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ravyn-lenae-enlists-childish-gambino-for-new-single-one-wish-3778661">招募了幼稚的甘比诺，以获得新的单曲“ One Wish”</a> 。</p> ;
